{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-05-19",
 "title": "Concussions in the Medbay",
 "summary": "After being knocked unconscious by Morganna during a botched brig interrogation, the pilot Bazil McKenzie wakes in the medbay with a concussion and a bandaged head, refusing to lie still as a nurse tries to restrain him. Bazil loudly demands to speak with Captain Darklighter and panics at the suggestion of possible brain damage, even tumbling off his bed in protest. Nearby, the equally battered Commander Kierv groans awake from his own head injuries, and the two trade dazed, sardonic complaints about the \"witch\" who put them there. Confined to the medbay under orders, Bazil gives up on the flustered nurse while Kierv, in too much pain to move, settles back to rest.",
